Sake

Premium Junmai 720ML
(Bottle)

Soto Sake, Premium Junmai
• Vegan
• Gluten Free
• No Additives
• No Added Sugar
• No Sulfites
• No Preservatives

The Junmai expression from SOTO is delicate and light in texture, acting as a chameleon; equally enjoyable chilled or warmed. Unlike many sakes in the Junmai category, SOTO is relatively low in acid and earthiness, making it an easy-drinking sake. This is the ideal sake for any and all occasions.
